    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean by \"accepting the dust\"? it sounds almost too peaceful, but it honestly just feels like giving up. is it actually okay to just stop trying to be okay? because it feels like the more i try, the more i just realize there's nothing left to save.",
